    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the time, starting up in April or May so-and-so, you're supposed to be indoors at 7 PM.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, of course, in the winter time, it was 6 PM, or 5, whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
